      "text": "Help me. My name is Sarah Jenkins. I lost my job last month and now I have a huge hospital bill. I'm behind on rent by two months and my landlord is threatening eviction. I don't know what to do."
    }
  ],
  "role": "user"
}

dataset.response_raw_json:
